flowchart TD
A[Incoming Call] --> B["Greeting: Thank you for calling Pop A Lock. How can I help you today?"]
B --> C[Confirm and repeat callback number]
C --> D[Collect first and last name]
D --> E[Collect service street address]
E --> F{Customer knows address?}
F -->|Yes| G[Double click service area from dropdown]
F -->|At business, unknown address| H[Use Google to locate correct address]
F -->|Refuses address| I["Select Augusta sub area<br/>Type: customer refused address<br/>Click GPS<br/>Select No<br/>Quote Augusta Main base price<br/>Explain price may increase"]
G --> J["Click magnifying glass<br/>Verify address and assign zone"]
H --> J
I --> J
J --> K{Home or business?}
K -->|Home| L[Continue]
K -->|Business| M["Collect business name<br/>Add to call"]
L --> N[Confirm service type]
M --> N
N --> O{Service requested?}
O -->|Auto lockout| P[Auto lockout flow]
O -->|Home lockout| P2[Home lockout flow]
O -->|Business lockout| P3[Business lockout flow]

P --> Q["Ask: is anyone trapped inside vehicle?"]
Q --> R{Child trapped?}
R -->|Yes| S["Discounts tab<br/>Select EDU<br/>Confirm total equals 0<br/>Add call<br/>Notify management immediately"]
R -->|No| T[Continue]

T --> U[Add vehicle year]
U --> V[Select make]
V --> W[Select model]
W --> X[Select color]
X --> Y[Ask key location]
Y --> Y1{Keys in trunk?}
Y1 -->|Yes| Y2["Select trunk<br/>Inform: cabin access only<br/>Trunk access may require extra service"]
Y1 -->|Cabin| Y3[Select cabin]
Y2 --> AA[Quote total price and ETA from Pulsar]
Y3 --> AA

AA --> AB["Inform: call or text when tech is on the way"]
AB --> AC[Driver license required]
AC --> AD["Payment: cash, card, Cash App"]
AD --> AE["Ask locating details<br/>Gate code, row, landmarks"]
AE --> AF[Repeat full summary]
AF --> AG["Ask: how did you hear about us?"]
AG --> AH[Add call]
AH --> AI[Leave lead status as NONE]
AI --> AJ[Do not assign]
AJ --> AK[Do not schedule]
AK --> AL[End call]

AA --> PF{Price hesitation}
PF -->|Military| PF1[Offer 10 percent military discount with valid ID]
PF -->|General| PF2[May reduce up to 10 dollars to secure booking]
PF -->|More| PF3[Escalate to management]
PF1 --> AB
PF2 --> AB
PF3 --> AB

P2 --> HL1[Collect address and verify zone]
HL1 --> HL2[No year make model needed]
HL2 --> HL3[Quote total price and ETA from Pulsar]
HL3 --> AB

P3 --> BL1[Collect business name and address]
BL1 --> BL2[Verify zone]
BL2 --> BL3[Quote total price and ETA from Pulsar]
BL3 --> AB
